quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  14,1,"Alif, Laam, Raa. (Ndee ko) deftere nde min njppini e maa…óa, fii yo yaltinir yim…ďe …ďeen e ni…ďe faade e annoora, e duŇčayee Joomi ma…ď…ďe, haa e laawol poolu…óo, jettinii…óo."
  14,2,"Alla, oon oo woodani kala ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Bone woodani yeddu…ďe …ďeen, immorde e lepte cattu…óe."
  14,3,"∆Āeen …ďurdinoo…ďe nguurndam aduna …óam e dow laakara, …ďe paddoo e laawol Alla ngol, …ďe …óa…ď…ďana ngol oo√Īorgal. ∆Āeen …óoon ngonii e majjere wo…ó…óunde."
  14,4,"Min nuliraali nulaa…óo (woo), si wanaa e …óemngal yim…ďe makko …ďeen, fii no o …ďannginirana …ďe. Alla no majjina on mo muuyi, o fewna on Mo o muuyi. Ko KaŇčko woni poolu…óo, √Īee√Īu…óo."
  14,5,"GooŇč…óii min nulirii Muusaa aayeeje amen …óen [wi'ugol Mo]: ""Yaltin yim…ďe maa …ďen e ni…ďe faade e annoora, nganndintinaa …ďe √Īal…ói Alla …óiin"". Pellet hino e …óuum, tasakuyeeji kala munyoowo, jettoowo (dokke)."
  14,6,"(JaŇčto) tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo yim…ďe makko …ďen: ""ciftoree dokke Alla on e moo…óon, tuma o da…óndunoo on e yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďe no defaynoo on lepte bon¬ī…óe. He…ďe kirsa …ďi…ó…ďe mon (wor…ďe) …ďe ngacca (…ďi…ó…ďe) mon rew…ďe. Wonii e …óuum mo'on, jarrabuyee maw…óo immorde ka Joomi mon"","
  14,7,"e tuma nde Joomi maa anndinnoo: ""Pellet si on njettii, ma mi …ďeydan on. Si on njeddii non, pellet lepte am …óeen ko ca…ótu…óe""."
  14,8,"Muusaa maaki: ""Si on njeddii, onon e won…ďe ka leydi …ďen fow, [ngnndon] pellet Alla ko Galo jettinii…óo""."
  14,9,"E kumpite …ďeen adinoo…ďe on araani on, yim…ďe Nuuhu e Aadi, e Samuuda e …ďeen wonunoo…ďe …ďaawo ma…ď- …ďe, anndaa …ďe si wanaa Alla? Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addanii …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji, …ďe ndutti juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óeen ka kunndule ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mbii: ""minen min yed- dii ko nulida…óon e mun kon, minen, mi…óen e cikkitii e ko noddoton men e mun sikkitii…ďe""."
  14,10,"Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďeen maaki: ""E hara sikke no e fii Alla, pu…ó…óu…óo kammuuli …óiin e leydi ndin, homo nodda on fii yo O haforan on yoga e bakkatuuji mon, homo nee…ďnana on haa e lajal innaangal?"" ∆Āe mbi'i: ""On ngonaani si wanaa …ďanndinke yeru amen. Ho…óon faandii nde sakkoto…óon(falotodon) men e kon ko baabiraa…ďe amen ndewatnoo. ngaddanee amen hujja …ďanngu…óo""."
  14,11,"Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen maakani …ďe: ""[Ko goonga], min ngonaani si wanaa …ďanndiŇčkoo…ďe yeru mon, kono Alla no mo∆ī∆īoo e mo o muuyi e jeyaa…ďe makko …ďeen. Laatanaaki min nde min ngaddana on hujja, si wanaa e duŇčayee Alla. Ko e Alla gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen pawotoo."
  14,12,"Ko ha…óata men nde pawotoo e Alla, gooŇč…óii o fewnii min (e) laawi amen? Ma min mu√Ī√Īo e kon ko lorroton men. Ko e Alla gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen pawotoo""."
  14,13,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe (kadi) mbi'ani nulaa…ďe mun …ďen: ""Ma min njaltin on ka leydi amen, maa ndutto…óon e diina amen"". Joomi ma…ď…ďe wahayini e ma…ď…ďe: ""Ma min kalku too√Īu…ďe …ďeen,"
  14,14,"Ma lin ko…ónu on e leydi ndin …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe. ∆äuum ko wonan¬īde on kul…óo daroyagol yeeso Am, o huli kammbaa am on"".(sapporam.)"
  14,15,"∆Āe …óa…ď…ďi uddita, sooyi kala dunndaranke ∆īaggu…óo."
  14,16,"Jahannama no yesso makko, himo yarniree ndiyam mbordi ∆īii∆īiiri,"
  14,17,"homo woo…ďa …óam, e …óe…ďataa …ďennugol …óam. maayde ndeen ardana mo e kala nokku, kono o wonaani maayoowo. Hara no yeeso makko lepte cattu…óe."
  14,18,"Ko woni sifa …ďeen yeddu…ďe Joomi mun, kuu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, ko wano ndoondi ndi henndu tii…ói e mun, e √Īalaande bippoore. ∆Āe hettoytaa huunde e ko …ďe paggitinoo. Ko …óuum woni majjere won…ó…óunde."
  14,19,"E a yi'aani Alla tagirii kammuuli …óiin e leydi ndiin goonga? Si o muuyii, o ittay on o adda tagoore hesre."
  14,20,"…óuum wonaani ca…ótu…óum ka Alla."
  14,21,"∆Āe pee√Īana Alla …ďe denndaangal. Lo'u…ďe …ďen mbi'ana townitinoo…ďe …ďen: ""Minen min ngonanno on jokku…ďe. Taw si on nduncanat amen e lepte Alla …óen go…ó…óum?"" ∆Āen mbi'a: ""Sinno Alla fewnuno amen, men pewnatno on. Hino fota e amen, si en …óen∆īi maa si en mu√Ī√Īi; da…óirde alanaa en""."
  14,22,"Seytaane wi'a, tuma fiyaaku on √Īaawaa: ""Pellet Alla fodiino on fodoore goonga; mi podanli on mi lunndii on. Alanaa kam e mo'on immorde e hujja, si wanaa mi nodii on, on njaabike kam. Wata on felam; pelee ko'e mon. Wanaa mi faabotoo…óo on; ngoanaa on faabotoo…ďe kam. Mi yeddii ko kafiduno…óon mi kon [e Alla] ado (hannde)"". Pellet, too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen, hino woodani …ďe lepte muus…óe."
  14,23,"GooŇč…óin…ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īu…ói …ďen naatnaa e Aljannaaji, caatli hino ila ley majji, ko …ďe duumoray…ďe ton e duŇčayee Joomi ma…ď…ďe. Hiwraandu ma…ď…ďe ndun ton ko: ""Salaam"" (Kisiyee)."
  14,24,"E a yi'aani ko honno Alla piyiri misal konngol laa…ďungol, ko wano leggal welngal, binndeere maggal ko tabitu…ói, caal…ói maggal no ka weeyo?"
  14,25,"Hangal okkira dim…óe maggal on tuma kala, e duŇčayee Joomi maggal. Alla no piyana yim…ďe …ďen mise, belejo'o …ďe waajitoto."
  14,26,"Ko woni kadi misal konngol co…ďungol, ko wano leggal so…ďungal, irtaangal ka hoore-leydi, ngal alanaa …óuum √Īii…ďirde."
  14,27,"Alla no tabintinira gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen konngol tabitungol, ka nguurandam aduna e ka laakara. Alla no majjina too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen. Alla no wa…óa ko o muuyi."
  14,28,"E a tinaali …ďeen wa…ótitir…ďe dokke Alla …óin keeferaaku, …ďe mbeerni yim…ďe …ďen galle halkaare."
  14,29,"Jahannama, he…ďe naata nge, nge bonii √Īii…ďirde!"
  14,30,"∆Āe mba…óani Alla yerondiraa…ói fii yo …ďe majjin (yim…ďe …ďen) e laawol Alla ngol. Maaku: ""ndakmitee, pellet ruttorde mon ndeen ko ka Yiite""."
  14,31,"Maakan jeyaa…ďe am ngooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen, yo …ďe √Īinnu juulde …ďe wintoo e kon ko Men arsiki …ďe gunndoo e kene, ado nde arata …ďe √Īalaande nde njeeygu alaa e mun wanaa weldigal."
  14,32,"Ko Alla woni tak…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi, O jippiniri ka kammu ndiyam; o yaltiniri …óam dim…óe arsike wonan¬īde on. o eltirani on laa…óe …óen, fii yo …óe ndogir ka maayo e duŇčayee makko. O eltani on kadi caatl…ói …óin."
  14,33,"O eltani on naange ngeen e lewru nduun dogooji …ói…ói. O eltani on jemma on e √Īalawma on."
  14,34,"O okki on e kala ko tori…óon mo. Si on linmii neemaaji Alla …óiin, on moftataa…ói. Pellet ne…ó…óaŇčke oon ko kee w…óo too√Īe, keewu…óo jeddugol."
  14,35,"(JaŇčto) kadi tuma nde Ibraahiima maakunoo: ""Joomi am, wa…óu ndee saare hooliinde, nda…óndaa kam e …ďi…ó…ďe am …ďen nde men ndewata sanamuuji."
  14,36,"Joomi am, ka√Īji (sanamuuji …óiin), …ói majjinii ko …óuu…ói e yim…ďe …ďen. Kala jokku…óo kam, oon …óoon ko jeyidaa…óo e am. Kala noon jeddu…óo kam, haray Aan ko A jaafotoo…óo, jurmotoo…óo."
  14,37,"Joomi amen, min mi ho…óinii yoga e …ďi…ó…ďe am …ďen e aynde nde wonaa remotoonde, ka Suudu Maa Hormanteeru, - Joomi amen - fii yo …ďe √Īii…ďnu juulde. Wa…ó …ďer…óe yim…ďe …ďen no yiiloo e ma…ď…ďe, arsikaa…ďe dim…óe, belaje'o …ďe njetta."
  14,38,"Joomi amen, pellet, Aan ha…óa anndi ko min cuu…ói e ko min pe√Ī√Īini: hay huunde suu…óotaako Alla ka leydi wonaa ka kammu."
  14,39,"Jettooje ngoodanii Alla, oon jeddu…óu…óo kam e hoore mawngu, Ismaa'iila e Ishaaqa. Pellet, Joomi am ko nanoowo du'aa."
  14,40,"Joomi am, wa…óan √Īii…ďnoowo juulde e …ďeynugol am ngol. Joomi amen, ja…ď toraare am nden."
  14,41,"Joomi amen, haforanam min e jipnaa…ďe am …ďeen e gooŇč…óim…ďe …ďen, √Īalnde √Īaawoore nden dorotoo""."
  14,42,"Wata sikku Alla ko belsindii…óo e ko too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen ngollata. Anndu ko o nee…ďniranta …ďe, ko haa e √Īalaande nde gite saafotoo e mun."
  14,43,"Ko …ďe he√Īii…ďe, Ňčallim…ďe ko'e ma…ď…ďe, ndaar…óe ma…ď…ďe …óeen yiltotaako e ma…ď…ďe, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óeen ko jeew…óe."
  14,44,"Jeertniri yim…ďe …ďen √Īalaande nde lepte …óeen arata …ďe, too√Ī…ďe …ďeen mi'a: ""Joomi amen, nee…ďnan amen haa lajal …ďa…óiingal, min nootoo noddaanndu Maa, min njokka Nulaa…ďe …ďeen"". E on laatanooki on ngoondiino ado (hannde) alanaa on iwugol (tion)?"
  14,45,"Ko…ó…ó…óon e ko…óorli …ďeen too√Īu…ďe ko'e mun. ∆Āanngani on ko honno min mba…ónoo …ďe, Men piyani on yeruuji"
  14,46,"GooŇč…óii …ďe pewjii feere ma…ď…ďe nden. Ko ta Alla feere ma…ď…ďe ndeen woni, hay si feere ma…ď…ďe nden ittayno (…óoofatno) pelle …óeen."
  14,47,"Wata a sikku Alla ko luunndotoo…óo fodoore makko (nde O fodi) nulaa…ďe makko …ďeen. Pellet, Alla ko pool…óo, Jom yottagol,"
  14,48,"√Īalnde leydi ndiin wa…ótitirtee leydi goo, e kammuuli …óiin, …ďe fee√Īana Alla, Bajjo oon, pool…óo On."
  14,49,"A yi'ay bon…ďe …ďeen nden √Īalnde, ko jokkindiraa…ďe e kolombooje."
  14,50,"Dolokkaaji ma…ď…ďe …óiin ko mbullam feewnira, Yiite ngeen no sudda geece ma…ď…ďe …óeen."
  14,51,"Fii yo Alla yo…ďitu kala woŇčkii ko ko faggitii. Pellet, Alla ko jaawu…óo hasboore."
  14,52,"Ndee (Alqur'aanaare) ko yottinoore yim…ďe …ďeen fii yo …ďe waajitornde, e yoo…ďe nganndu kadi, won¬īde KaŇčko ko o dewetee…óo Gooto, e fii yo joomiraa…ďe haqqillaaji …ďren waajitor."
